Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.11,0:01:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达高度  长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发动机怎么样?\N没问题  长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.05,0:01:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,负载过重了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.71,0:01:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  长官  应该没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.52,0:01:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他认为盔甲将会复活了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无法维持高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正在围着山转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简要的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们别无选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫无疑问  那个盔甲是我们族的关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.17,0:02:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们必须把它带给弗肯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保持冷静！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一个敌人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀了他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在干什么?敌人只有一个人而已！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.03,0:03:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会这样?  只是他一个人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.25,0:04:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你就是我们听说很久的龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要杀光我所有的敌人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙盔甲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从你的长眠中醒过来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字是艾斯卡弗洛尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的盔甲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又在睡觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.63,0:07:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃学出来就为了睡觉?  小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了个梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是关于我的童年的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.51,0:07:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦  你很久以前告诉我的那个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在东京站看到的那个男人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个男人穿着奇怪的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白日梦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么我现在还会梦见那个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你很寂寞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.09,0:07:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多出去走走找个男朋友吧  小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你无事可做才会做那种梦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.67,0:07:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么不加入我们社团?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.77,0:07:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我从田径社退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会觉得非常尴尬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,社员都很想你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要  太累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外  我的腿也受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了  我就是傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊?收件人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你这样不安?还给我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我还要改写！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是收件人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还给我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤嘉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“致亲爱的尤嘉莉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.21,0:08:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要死了  再见  尤嘉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...神崎瞳”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一点写信的天赋都没有  内容也乏味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我静一静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要留下这些遗言死去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不然作为你的朋友我会很羞愧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了  别担心  我可是个十足的胆小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.63,0:09:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如你想自杀  让我最先知道  可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会陪你一起死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要  没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会努力活下去  直到头发斑白的老婆婆...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...一直活到该我离去的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明天会跟我去  对不对?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,约定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?  我说过  早上记得叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最近经常上课打瞌睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么早上起不来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你晚上出去了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.44,0:09:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.21,0:09:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是觉得很困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什么时候都觉得很困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许我出了什么问题?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会这样呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是我太疲倦了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家看起来都很有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才经常睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.13,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡觉时  我可以慢慢死去……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且大家都不会注意到  我的死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过什么都没有变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.47,0:10:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我死了也不会改变什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.75,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注意  代代木站发生了事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们为对您带来的不便而表示歉意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们将尽快恢复原状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们为对您带来的不便而表示歉意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里出了事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么都做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿  等下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.97,0:11:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳  你最近几天一直很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退出田径社  逃避所有事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.82,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟老师解释你退出的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很好  不用为我担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.23,0:11:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就让我静一静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样呀....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.47,0:11:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得走了  那么  明天学校见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样死去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样死去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伤害朋友的讨厌家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样死去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁可以...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.86,0:12:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样  让所有事都消亡吧……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让这个悲伤的世界呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让所有事都消亡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.78,0:12:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一样的人呀..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从这个世界之外..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来加入我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被选中的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.57,0:12:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我吗?..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.97,0:12:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是翼女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.87,0:13:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你将会实现世界的预言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的世界  盖亚……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是梦吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是幻象?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.58,0:13:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  这是真的  我的梦想成真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻之月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是多么美丽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难怪她被称为厄运的盔甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她只招致厄运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以  所有人都来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙盔甲将要复活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蜜拉娜  是飞船！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是黑龙族吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向我们来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像我预测的  对不对?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好为此好好报答我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.14,0:16:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我简直不能等待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长  我们真的能把它射下来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要担心梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许你太高估了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.09,0:17:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人  梵大人  梵大人  ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.05,0:17:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射下来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷  开炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它还活着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.94,0:19:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?停下来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.69,0:19:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底发生什么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁来救救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.38,0:19:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.05,0:19:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是...  你是翼女神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是翼女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是龙族的后代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我恳求你  翼女神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我在盖亚世界里服侍你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.04,0:20:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶艾斯卡弗洛尼后  我将会除掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有违背你意志的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.01,0:20:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样死去吧……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.85,0:20:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在哪?这里是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾斯卡弗洛尼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.61,0:20:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾斯卡弗洛尼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.83,0:21:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.29,0:21:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.09,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你让它走的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.27,0:21:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么藏在龙盔甲里面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.64,0:21:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.31,0:21:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快点回答他  小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.55,0:22:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.28,0:22:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是黑龙族的忍者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.86,0:22:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  让我杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.46,0:22:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下  梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要阻止我  亚连
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.87,0:22:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个女人  你还不能杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.40,0:22:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这个家伙放走了龙盔甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.91,0:22:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许是  也许不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.31,0:22:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让她活着吧  她也许对咱们有用处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.08,0:22:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外  我不想看到女人的血喷出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.01,0:22:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要教我做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.66,0:22:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会杀了任何挡住我路的人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.09,0:22:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,试试吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.86,0:22:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.40,0:22:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们俩做什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.52,0:23:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵  住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.59,0:23:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果队长认真的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在已经是个死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.53,0:23:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盖蒂茨  用小刀太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.60,0:23:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没打到重要位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.50,0:23:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好你没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盖蒂茨  你在被公主责骂吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到这儿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.95,0:23:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起  长官  我只是在开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.82,0:23:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿！那是个女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.39,0:23:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人?  真的是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.92,0:23:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看她的短头发我还以为是个男的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.02,0:23:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵肯定是从哪儿把她抓过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.97,0:24:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是远古时代预言的传说中的翼女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.71,0:24:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是将要把盖亚带领到一个新世界的人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.18,0:24:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢天谢地！谢天谢地！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.78,0:24:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴  你这讨厌的算命人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.52,0:24:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚连  这个女孩就是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.85,0:24:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.59,0:24:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个女孩是翼女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.06,0:24:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过她从长相来说也跟我们没什么区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.26,0:24:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿  梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.70,0:24:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.60,0:24:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵  我随时随地都会和你决斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.61,0:24:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要找梵大人的碴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.45,0:24:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恶棍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.51,0:24:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.32,0:24:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...你在流血！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.35,0:24:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个混帐  你老让梵大人做危险的事情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.32,0:24:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪天一定会毒死你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.13,0:25:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神  请不要担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.33,0:25:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们欢迎您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.34,0:25:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过天堂的旅行你一定很困乏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.17,0:25:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请在我们的房屋里休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.38,0:25:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赐予我们龙的力量与翼的庇护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.31,0:25:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.35,0:25:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加入我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.20,0:25:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你吗  迪恩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.70,0:25:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.10,0:25:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是为什么神旨没有指定你来继承王位的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.61,0:25:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会用自己的双手杀掉梵的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.55,0:25:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.76,0:26:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.77,0:26:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.77,0:26:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.44,0:26:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是她到另一个龙的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.88,0:27:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一条龙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.82,0:27:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵  是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.76,0:27:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神去那个混帐的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.00,0:27:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无法感觉到龙盔甲的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.37,0:27:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.24,0:27:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有龙和翼女神两个的共鸣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.14,0:27:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙盔甲不会复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.14,0:27:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是唯一可以和翼女神共鸣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.15,0:27:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.89,0:27:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙盔甲将会毁坏整个盖亚世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:41.52,0:27:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.46,0:27:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.13,0:27:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是我真实的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.99,0:28:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨拉丝国王为了保存他的生命来信恳求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:19.86,0:28:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑龙族不需要奴隶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.16,0:28:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是弗肯指挥官的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.17,0:28:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这里移为平地不要留下活口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.21,0:28:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多么残暴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.74,0:28:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,征服之后  他们就把村庄夷为平地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:37.11,0:28:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连无辜的动物也不放过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.51,0:28:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后紧接着屠杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:43.15,0:28:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多么残忍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.46,0:28:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.46,0:28:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还担心你会死了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.37,0:29:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还不能让你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.04,0:29:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.05,0:29:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是个梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:15.48,0:29:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是梦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.15,0:29:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有都是梦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:18.32,0:29:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必须要醒过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:22.66,0:29:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.99,0:29:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦?这不是梦哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:29.23,0:29:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我来\N不！不要！住手!求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:31.70,0:29:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.76,0:30:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.73,0:30:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阳光让你精神起来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.80,0:30:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.44,0:30:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们得让你在这里待一会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.47,0:30:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到我们确认你是真的翼女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.14,0:30:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.81,0:30:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.82,0:30:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看起来真的不像个女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.32,0:30:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:29.69,0:30:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何  告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.03,0:30:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:34.76,0:30:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.70,0:30:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神崎瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.43,0:30:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:42.60,0:30:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听起来很可爱  真是个好名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:45.54,0:30:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫蜜拉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.98,0:30:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在盖亚世界中我们被称为阿巴哈拉其
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.88,0:30:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.41,0:30:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都是被黑龙摧毁国家的幸存者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:54.68,0:30:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是我们与他们斗争的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.02,0:30:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斗争?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:58.52,0:31:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾斯卡弗洛尼是战争之神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:01.06,0:31:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他将会一直在我们这边来帮助我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:05.46,0:31:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是吟游诗人告诉我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.56,0:31:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“翼女神将会使艾斯卡弗洛尼复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:12.20,0:31:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从幻之月降临”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.00,0:31:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你从艾斯卡弗洛尼出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.51,0:31:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.74,0:31:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.48,0:31:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.08,0:31:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:28.68,0:31:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.52,0:31:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.53,0:31:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我们没什么好吃的  但是你要吃点什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.96,0:31:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不  不用...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.53,0:31:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.63,0:31:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是如果...\N什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.37,0:31:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.77,0:31:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:48.77,0:31:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能喝点水吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.07,0:31:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.08,0:31:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事情  你为什么不早说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:58.35,0:31:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.81,0:32:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果翼女神真的存在的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.25,0:32:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望她会赐予咱们好的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:06.15,0:32:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只要想要好酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.56,0:32:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长真的相信吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.26,0:32:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.86,0:32:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基耀  你怎么想?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.10,0:32:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.70,0:32:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还从没见过真正的翼女神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.03,0:32:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是就是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.14,0:32:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.73,0:32:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的看起来那么奇怪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:49.96,0:32:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的  她看起来不像这个世界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.17,0:32:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果她是真的  黑龙族...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:58.94,0:33:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...会来杀了她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.31,0:33:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不能将翼女神交给他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.45,0:33:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵  你保护她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:08.32,0:33:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不相信她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.18,0:33:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在害怕吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.89,0:33:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果她是真的翼女神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.89,0:33:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...龙盔甲会再次出现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.09,0:33:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果传说是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.00,0:33:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...艾斯卡弗洛尼会嗜血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.03,0:33:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙族的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.67,0:33:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是龙族最后一个国王  梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.50,0:33:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.21,0:33:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我迷路了  我在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.55,0:33:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.69,0:33:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.66,0:33:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊..这是什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.20,0:33:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.23,0:33:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.47,0:34:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:03.07,0:34:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...我在找水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.54,0:34:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.78,0:34:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你需要水  为什么不去巷道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:10.75,0:34:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我不认识路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.43,0:34:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真奇怪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:28.16,0:34:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是什么话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:30.50,0:34:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:32.03,0:34:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.44,0:34:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是翼女神吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.98,0:34:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:43.95,0:34:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该知道的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.25,0:34:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我连我在哪儿都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.19,0:34:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太荒谬了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:55.62,0:34:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在觉得精疲力尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.53,0:35:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看起来没有那么累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:03.36,0:35:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.30,0:35:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算命的  你怎么会在这儿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:07.20,0:35:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两个年轻女孩的声音就像引啼的小鸟...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.54,0:35:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...把我带进一个欢快的氛围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:13.11,0:35:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啰嗦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:15.91,0:35:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐  我是否有荣幸看看这块宝石?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:20.35,0:35:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宝石?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.58,0:35:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.05,0:35:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.32,0:35:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个美丽的宝石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.99,0:35:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该好好保管它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.63,0:35:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以看看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.74,0:35:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:47.94,0:35:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从来没有想过你的手艺这么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.94,0:35:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的嘴也很甜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.45,0:35:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何  他是个算命师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:53.35,0:35:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个真残忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.18,0:35:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.73,0:36:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:05.93,0:36:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.66,0:36:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在  如果你想付钱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.60,0:36:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疼  疼  疼....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.04,0:36:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准在这里讲钱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:38.13,0:36:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当梵大人还年轻的时候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:40.80,0:36:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...他的国家被黑龙族摧毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:43.76,0:36:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的同伴呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.90,0:36:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不是应该一起战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.24,0:36:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在战场上相遇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.41,0:36:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...并且从那以来一直在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.24,0:36:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他们就像伙伴一样  对不对?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:54.58,0:36:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:56.11,0:36:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人一直独自一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.02,0:37:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.19,0:37:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是很奇怪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:09.02,0:37:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人注定要成为国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.49,0:37:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使他的国家和人民所有的大家都离去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:17.40,0:37:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只要还活着就必须和敌人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.10,0:37:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是梵大人作为国王的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.27,0:37:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是  实际上  他是个仁慈宽厚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.45,0:37:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我看到过他的这一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.46,0:37:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿咧?这个不是国王?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.93,0:37:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  你不是和那个可爱的女孩在一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.80,0:37:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论什么时候都是个高傲的家伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:53.17,0:37:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不能接受帮助  因为他是个国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.39,0:38:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那个吗?贾久卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:21.56,0:38:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯指挥官想要从这里通过所有的东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.14,0:38:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样?  西石塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.44,0:38:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的  长官  我看看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:36.58,0:38:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...最下层的甲板  右侧一个穿白衣的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.58,0:38:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.98,0:38:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿白衣的女孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.65,0:38:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪兰度大人  我们必须启动这个计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.22,0:38:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只需要抓住翼女神  对不对?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.93,0:38:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.43,0:38:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.73,0:38:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们为什么不把他们全杀了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.23,0:38:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿巴哈拉其可是职业战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.57,0:39:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果因为我们无视命令而损失太多人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.54,0:39:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别喋喋不休了  天变黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.15,0:39:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.65,0:39:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.82,0:39:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚连！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.35,0:39:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑龙的骑兵来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.22,0:39:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来我们不能按时到达多鲁希娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.74,0:40:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪兰度大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.04,0:40:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的进攻只是个虚晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:12.17,0:40:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请记住  长官！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.24,0:40:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:14.58,0:40:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪兰度大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:21.98,0:40:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让他们进去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.42,0:40:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀光见到的所有人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:27.45,0:40:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们冲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:29.79,0:40:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保持距离！别散开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.67,0:40:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么了?  我们好像停下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.14,0:40:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:48.71,0:40:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手  你...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:50.91,0:40:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:55.25,0:40:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐！  他们行动的太快了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:15.44,0:41:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅露露！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.14,0:41:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅露露！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.57,0:41:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睁开眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:20.24,0:41:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅露露！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:22.58,0:41:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:23.68,0:41:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:38.39,0:41:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令要求的是佯攻而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.63,0:41:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他被追杀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.73,0:42:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:16.50,0:42:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.23,0:42:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你保持安静  我不会杀你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.84,0:42:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.55,0:42:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦  是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.61,0:42:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别离开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:37.18,0:42:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走开  奴库希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.35,0:42:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你吗  梵大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:42.12,0:42:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是梵大人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.86,0:42:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你会在人类的战斗中?！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:47.56,0:42:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你们氏族的习俗吗?！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.23,0:42:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人类把我们拉进战争的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.27,0:42:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑龙族摧毁了你们的土地...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.24,0:43:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的村庄现在已成灰烬...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.97,0:43:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...幸存者都被俘获了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.28,0:43:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们这种牧游部落从不想和好战的人类开战！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.82,0:43:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是为了救我们的人民...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:11.29,0:43:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...我们和黑龙族做了个交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:14.25,0:43:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们用她来和我们人民的生命交换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.06,0:43:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人  我们需要她！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.86,0:43:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能让你这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.20,0:43:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧  奴库希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.60,0:43:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想和你战斗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:28.67,0:43:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.27,0:43:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奴库希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:40.45,0:43:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  我打错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.75,0:43:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了  反正他也没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.46,0:43:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾久卡  我们只是要抓那个女孩是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.13,0:43:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不需要那个男的  是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.09,0:43:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我可以按我喜欢的做  是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:02.04,0:44:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:13.58,0:44:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.68,0:44:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个家伙有魔力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.42,0:44:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散开点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:34.77,0:44:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘记了你是和阿巴哈拉其在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:42.51,0:44:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:43.98,0:44:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...你是我听说很久的龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:49.08,0:44:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种力量...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.95,0:44:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳！  躲在我身后！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.82,0:44:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:02.43,0:45:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦  讨厌  我湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:06.90,0:45:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我讨厌雨...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:09.07,0:45:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...雨让我情绪失落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:12.91,0:45:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的一个部下刚才死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:16.04,0:45:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他是个笨蛋  该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:19.15,0:45:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你强大  就不用死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:22.62,0:45:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在  该开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:25.45,0:45:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我们玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:27.75,0:45:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:26.18,0:46:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白翼...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:37.86,0:46:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:39.03,0:46:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:42.00,0:46:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:44.03,0:46:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你  梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:45.97,0:46:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会有一点点不舒服不过马上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:47.73,0:46:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓紧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.19,0:47:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:08.79,0:47:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵  你怎么了  梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.99,0:47:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翅膀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:17.50,0:47:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:21.87,0:47:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:24.00,0:47:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么伤的这么重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:27.21,0:47:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行  停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:30.18,0:47:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要流血了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:32.21,0:47:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵！  振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.91,0:47:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睁开眼睛啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:35.75,0:47:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:37.58,0:47:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有没有人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:39.89,0:47:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:41.66,0:47:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有人来帮帮我们！救救梵啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:45.26,0:47:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:46.79,0:47:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来人啊！救命啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:49.36,0:47:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来帮帮梵...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:53.03,0:47:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:56.90,0:47:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让这个男人自由吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:59.21,0:48:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从独自战斗的悲痛中解脱出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:02.14,0:48:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他寻求死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:04.44,0:48:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死亡就是安宁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:07.05,0:48:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:09.75,0:48:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲伤从不会停止...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.42,0:48:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...直到死亡的降临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:18.13,0:48:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想死吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:21.09,0:48:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:22.63,0:48:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他那么悲伤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.53,0:48:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他那么痛苦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.37,0:48:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:28.97,0:48:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你一个人忍受悲伤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.87,0:48:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你并不孤独  梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:37.34,0:48:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要梵活下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:44.42,0:48:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会陪着他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:48.62,0:48:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到他发现他并不是孤独一人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:51.43,0:48:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到他不再悲伤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:53.63,0:48:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...我一直都会陪伴在他的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:56.36,0:48:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲伤是会停止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:00.97,0:49:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:03.74,0:49:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像雨最终还是会停...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:05.94,0:49:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...我们也会看到蓝天显露出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:19.59,0:49:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你不遵守我的命令  迪兰度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:24.46,0:49:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我让你把翼女神带回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:28.93,0:49:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你反而让你自己深陷在无用的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:32.60,0:49:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:47.95,0:49:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁救了你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:50.22,0:49:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...当你与野狗无处可归时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:53.19,0:49:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁救了你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:58.96,0:50:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是弗肯大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:00.99,0:50:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁给了你龙族骑兵的指挥权?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:04.66,0:50:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:08.27,0:50:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是弗肯大人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:10.40,0:50:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:15.88,0:50:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让我失望  迪兰度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:25.45,0:50:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是盖亚中极少数幸存的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:27.35,0:50:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...拥有龙族血脉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:30.86,0:50:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你很年轻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:32.53,0:50:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...但是血脉会带来魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:34.96,0:50:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对你的力量给予厚望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:38.87,0:50:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:40.50,0:50:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪兰度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:42.14,0:50:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...如果你需要  我会给你新的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:46.91,0:50:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,适合于龙族后裔的新力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.84,0:50:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要新力量...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:12.40,0:51:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯指挥官的另一个预言成真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:15.94,0:51:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知德莱甸长官这里的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:19.14,0:51:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉他盔甲已经聚集在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:20.71,0:51:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:21.94,0:51:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:23.34,0:51:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我越看它  它越让人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.61,0:51:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的盔甲  在多鲁希娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:32.82,0:51:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是德莱甸给的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:35.72,0:51:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是不知道小瞳和梵在哪儿吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:38.69,0:51:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.59,0:51:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯将会前去多鲁希娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:43.13,0:51:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要快点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.83,0:51:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信他们仍然活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:47.66,0:51:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵会和小瞳一起来多鲁希娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:06.55,0:52:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您吃过饭了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:10.25,0:52:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是  已经吃过了  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:13.22,0:52:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你衣服还得洗洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:16.79,0:52:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在还要再等一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:19.19,0:52:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道怎么感谢你的好意  为什么帮助我们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:23.33,0:52:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚当国的人民从来不拒绝帮助陌生人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:27.90,0:52:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能见梵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:30.81,0:52:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还在睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:34.14,0:52:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:35.58,0:52:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:48.16,0:52:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:51.79,0:52:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请安心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:53.73,0:52:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经驱走了恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:56.50,0:52:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过还需要一些时间...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:59.70,0:53:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...直到伤口完全痊愈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:03.31,0:53:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此之前  你就在我们的村庄里好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:10.21,0:53:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.22,0:53:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人出来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:54.69,0:53:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摧毁了我国家的那个人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:56.93,0:53:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...是我的哥哥迪恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:59.23,0:54:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在黑龙族的名字是弗肯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:02.03,0:54:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:04.07,0:54:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:05.60,0:54:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的国家  神旨决定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.27,0:54:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...到底国王的哪个儿子继承王位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:11.37,0:54:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神意指明我来继位  而不是我哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:14.91,0:54:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就为了这个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:18.21,0:54:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为我们王族的仅存者...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:21.48,0:54:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...唯一支持我活下来的理由...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:24.09,0:54:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...就是杀了我哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:28.76,0:54:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道自己要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:31.73,0:54:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:34.26,0:54:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:37.77,0:54:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道这有多痛苦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:40.24,0:54:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...过着杀人与被杀的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:43.84,0:54:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我变得非常混乱以至于失去了生活的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:48.68,0:54:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想静静死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:52.01,0:54:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和梵一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:55.82,0:54:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:57.32,0:54:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...这就是我为什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.99,0:55:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...想陪伴在你的身边的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.13,0:55:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:04.96,0:55:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...要跟着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:23.77,0:56:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你的帮助  卢姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:26.04,0:56:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:27.08,0:56:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯  你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:29.95,0:56:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听说多鲁希娜正在被黑龙族围攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:34.18,0:56:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:35.62,0:56:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是  我的朋友在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:39.25,0:56:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愿龙的力量时刻保护你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:42.66,0:56:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊  希望你以后还会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:45.16,0:56:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我向梅露露问好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:46.93,0:56:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记得回来哦  到时候我们一起唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:49.16,0:56:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常感谢你们哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:51.07,0:56:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家多多保重哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:54.04,0:56:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧  小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:58.61,0:57:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保重  姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:02.91,0:57:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:36.24,0:57:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德莱甸先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:37.45,0:57:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:38.35,0:57:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他来自多鲁希娜一个富有的家庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:40.22,0:57:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是阿巴哈拉其的资助人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:43.05,0:57:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可以从他那里知道亚连的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:18.82,0:58:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了  坐下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:21.29,0:58:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯..嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:31.47,0:58:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多么动人的歌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:33.30,0:58:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是古代龙族的歌谣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:34.77,0:58:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?梵知道这首歌?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:37.51,0:58:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:38.44,0:58:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我妈妈在我小的时候唱过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:43.51,0:58:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在黑暗中  龙醒来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:46.82,0:58:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有冰冷麻木的心  巨龙咆哮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:50.22,0:58:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有你伴我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:52.45,0:58:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨龙又沉睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:54.66,0:58:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当巨龙得到翅膀的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:56.99,0:58:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飞向天空  我们的希望也随之飞翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:03.80,0:59:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:04.83,0:59:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:06.13,0:59:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿  陌生人  你们好啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:07.77,0:59:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们喜欢我们的音乐吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:10.97,0:59:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己更喜欢一些愉快的音乐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:14.34,0:59:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是  就如你所见  整个村庄充斥着令人厌烦的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:18.55,0:59:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有什么快乐的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:21.32,0:59:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想见德莱甸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:22.95,0:59:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德莱甸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:24.35,0:59:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:25.85,0:59:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个酒店的老板是德莱甸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:28.42,0:59:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不是黑龙族的奸细吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:32.23,0:59:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:33.33,0:59:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们到这里来是为了见阿巴哈拉其的亚连
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:35.66,0:59:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放轻松点  看看你四周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:39.13,0:59:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿巴哈拉其正在黑龙族追捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:43.64,0:59:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的像亚连说的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:46.47,0:59:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,热血的梵大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:48.94,0:59:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这个可爱的小姐一定就是翼女神  小瞳了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:53.78,0:59:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是这个酒店的老板  德莱甸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.69,0:59:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:58.59,0:59:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅露露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:59.22,1:00:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅露露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:00.39,1:00:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人  我一直非常担心你啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.56,1:00:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:12.17,1:00:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔导士已经开始了龙盔甲复活的仪式
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.57,1:00:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盔甲是从湖底找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:18.24,1:00:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在盔甲复活  只是个时间问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:22.74,1:00:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那个该死的东西复活了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.48,1:00:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...我们就没希望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:26.28,1:00:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们和整个多鲁希娜都会被毁掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.92,1:00:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们最后一张王牌就是艾斯卡弗洛尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.25,1:00:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要不要问一下翼女神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:35.56,1:00:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会试试的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.63,1:00:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我真的是翼女神的话我一定会帮助你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:45.63,1:00:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这真的就像歌谣里所唱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:48.50,1:00:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“翼女神使龙盔甲复活...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:52.27,1:00:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...然后带领盖亚到一个新世界”
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:55.81,1:00:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:57.21,1:00:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这首歌还有下文
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.38,1:01:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“龙盔甲将会摧毁整个盖亚世界...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:03.55,1:01:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...然后消失”
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:05.09,1:01:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古盖亚就是被龙盔甲摧毁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:09.72,1:01:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神就是召唤艾斯卡弗洛尼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:15.23,1:01:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是到这里来摧毁盖亚的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:22.10,1:01:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在多鲁希娜的军队都已经进入战斗位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:25.07,1:01:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有的管道入口都被封住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.31,1:01:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿巴哈拉其士兵是不会突破我们的防线
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:31.01,1:01:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加快盔甲复活仪式
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:33.08,1:01:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:36.75,1:01:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个新盔甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:39.19,1:01:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你指挥这么多军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:41.99,1:01:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你还要更多的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:45.29,1:01:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:48.96,1:01:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:50.43,1:01:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,召唤翼女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.07,1:01:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:56.30,1:01:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:15.19,1:02:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肮脏的龙血会使龙盔甲复活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.24,1:02:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.21,1:02:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么能..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:36.08,1:02:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歇斯塔  有来自指挥官的命令吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:38.75,1:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:42.62,1:02:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果迪兰度大人出了什么事情的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.85,1:02:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会杀光所有的魔导士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.47,1:03:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  那是什么声音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:00.34,1:03:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是从连接柱发出的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.44,1:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:08.98,1:03:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事  梅露露
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:11.01,1:03:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:12.61,1:03:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼睛看起来好温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:15.55,1:03:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:16.35,1:03:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的!我能看出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:27.20,1:03:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵大人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:29.66,1:03:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅露露  在战斗结束以后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:33.03,1:03:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...我们就回亚当的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:34.47,1:03:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:36.30,1:03:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:37.21,1:03:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的话  所有事情都会结束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:40.11,1:03:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样  我也能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:43.14,1:03:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是到这里来摧毁盖亚的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:53.39,1:03:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊咧?..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:09.07,1:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:12.01,1:04:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.47,1:04:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:15.81,1:04:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请选择摧毁盖亚的途径
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:19.25,1:04:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样盖亚所有的痛苦就会消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:22.42,1:04:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切事物的终点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:24.49,1:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我不能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:28.66,1:04:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:30.33,1:04:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使这个世界所有的悲伤都不复存在吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:33.06,1:04:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯大人..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:35.16,1:04:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请救救他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:45.64,1:04:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是她在叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:47.91,1:04:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵!小瞳不见了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.98,1:04:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:51.31,1:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不在自己的房间?这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:54.18,1:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有不祥的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:56.62,1:04:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:58.09,1:04:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是弗肯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:59.85,1:05:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:27.12,1:05:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:36.19,1:05:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等这一刻已经很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:40.36,1:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是弗肯先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:42.63,1:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了消除所有的悲伤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:45.03,1:05:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我恳求你让我能驾驶艾斯卡弗洛尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:50.61,1:05:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:52.14,1:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:53.71,1:05:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你确实希望结束这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:57.48,1:05:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:58.85,1:06:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有这么想!
