Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:41.72,1:22:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是我来这里的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:44.15,1:22:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:47.59,1:22:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:52.26,1:22:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算毁灭盖亚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:54.66,1:22:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:56.73,1:22:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...也不会终结你的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:59.63,1:23:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别对我说教
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:02.60,1:23:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最大的悲伤就是你  梵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:11.31,1:23:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:13.18,1:23:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我唯一的渴望就是亲手杀掉你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.29,1:23:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在  作为龙族的国王...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:22.16,1:23:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...我要求你与我决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:24.22,1:23:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:26.06,1:23:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也不想战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:28.36,1:23:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  你就这里死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:57.56,1:23:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳!小瞳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:00.56,1:24:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事  梵
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:03.30,1:24:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.37,1:24:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可怜的人  我的灵魂也是破碎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:11.61,1:24:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能感受到其它人的痛苦和悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:15.54,1:24:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以为我是一个人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:18.91,1:24:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是我为什么回应你  让你来到这个世界的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:23.65,1:24:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是现在不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:25.69,1:24:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你难道不明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:27.85,1:24:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梵的悲伤  梵的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:32.59,1:24:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是带给梵悲伤的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:36.26,1:24:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:38.13,1:24:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个世界充满悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:41.20,1:24:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了挣脱命运的轮回只有彻底消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:46.21,1:24:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是我为什么有那种希望...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:49.21,1:24:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...并且堕落我自己的翅膀的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:53.81,1:24:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:56.12,1:24:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:59.45,1:25:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会满足你的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:18.67,1:25:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:21.91,1:25:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了被你压迫摧毁的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:23.78,1:25:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯指挥官...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:31.52,1:25:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,复仇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:35.36,1:25:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗肯先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:43.96,1:25:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:45.33,1:25:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.20,1:25:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要靠近!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:49.80,1:25:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:53.21,1:25:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:56.68,1:25:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我遗忘很久的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:22.47,1:26:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:25.91,1:26:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在弗肯大人死后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:28.44,1:26:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个城堡就会瓦解
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:31.28,1:26:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个从这个悲伤的地方走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:36.52,1:26:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:38.42,1:26:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会陪着弗肯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:47.29,1:26:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,城堡在崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:26.37,1:27:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:31.37,1:27:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙族的人们在歌舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:39.31,1:27:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翼女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:13.68,1:28:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强大的黑龙族垮掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:19.02,1:28:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在应该去哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:21.72,1:28:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有战争了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:25.03,1:28:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:57.02,1:29:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  梵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:59.05,1:30:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能在这里待多久?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:02.89,1:30:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到幻之月把你叫回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:06.96,1:30:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此之前  我会陪着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:11.93,1:30:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:15.34,1:30:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们永远在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:44.36,1:30:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:46.57,1:30:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能听到那首歌吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:35.78,1:31:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随着我泪水的溢出
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:42.62,1:31:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能从模糊的视线中看清你最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:50.43,1:31:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要走!不要离开我!在这里陪着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:55.67,1:32:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阳光从天空中射出
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:11.02,1:32:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是如此无足轻重
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:18.26,1:32:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我全心全意的爱着你  比任何人都要爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:25.70,1:32:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:29.34,1:32:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:33.07,1:32:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么多珍贵的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:40.25,1:32:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那时  我只是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:42.92,1:32:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长年累月地注视着烟雾与幻象
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:46.52,1:32:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要忘记...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:51.89,1:32:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是孤单一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:56.40,1:33:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我们天各一方  我们的手也是紧紧相连的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:07.24,1:33:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的初恋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:17.82,1:33:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我初次尝到悲伤的苦涩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:28.23,1:33:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使有什么会消失  也一定有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:32.30,1:33:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么会再度孕育
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:38.81,1:33:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们分开的时候你给我的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:43.98,1:33:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我最大的满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:54.32,1:34:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某天我们一定会重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:00.69,1:34:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后一直在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:05.43,1:34:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论多远  我们会注视着对方的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:15.98,1:34:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用我们所有的希望和梦想做赌注
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:26.62,1:34:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们立下誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:31.99,1:34:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心存
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:36.83,1:34:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感动的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:41.73,1:34:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起生活在幸福的明天

